org.forgerock.openig.servlet
Class ServletSession

java.lang.Object
  org.forgerock.openig.servlet.ServletSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
Session, ReadableMap<String,Object>, WritableMap<String,Object>
public class ServletSession
extends Object
implements Session

Exposes the session managed by the servlet container as an exchange session. This implementation will get a servlet session if already allocated, otherwise will not create one until an attempt is made to put an attribute in it.
